    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any natural, treated or man-made material with the appearance but not the composition, structure or physical and optical properties of a diamond. Use "synthetic diamonds" when referring to the artificial product with the same physical and chemical properties.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
